'''An Yeong-han''' (born 27 November 1917) was a South Korean [[Sport of athletics|athlete]]. He competed in the [[Athletics at the 1948 Summer Olympics – Men's discus throw|men's discus throw]] at the [[1948 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/an/an-yeong-han-1.html |title=An Yeong-han Olympic Results |accessdate=11 January 2018}}</ref>
